1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:05,250
A mysterious figure visits a quiet town, stirring up old secrets and fears.

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:09,200
A quiet town street with fog rolling in as night falls.

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:17,450
A mysterious figure dressed entirely in black walks down the deserted road towards the old lighthouse, their face hidden by a dark hooded cloak.

4
00:00:17,450 --> 00:00:20,737
The interior of an old newspaper office.

5
00:00:20,737 --> 00:00:29,112
A young journalist named Lily is going through old files and newspapers from the past, looking for any mention of the lighthouse or mysterious visitors.

6
00:00:29,112 --> 00:00:32,475
A rainy night scene at the abandoned lighthouse.

7
00:00:32,475 --> 00:00:38,512
The door creaks open to reveal a dark, fog-filled interior as lightning strikes outside.

8
00:00:38,512 --> 00:00:46,962
A crowded town square at night where townspeople gather around whispering and pointing towards the direction of the lighthouse, looking anxious and uneasy.

9
00:00:46,962 --> 00:00:53,450
Inside the dusty attic of the old lighthouse, Lily discovers an old diary hidden behind a loose floorboard.

10
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:59,087
She sits on the wooden floor, reading about love, loss, and secrets from long ago.

11
00:00:59,087 --> 00:01:04,787
As the sun rises on the day after the next visit, the mystery deepens rather than resolves.

12
00:01:04,787 --> 00:01:15,325
The journalist finds an old diary in the lighthouse that hints at a tragic love story from decades ago, suggesting the cloaked figure is an apparition tied to unresolved emotions and forgotten history.

